{"version":"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1","title":"windows - Tag | SPAWN2PWN","description":"Hugo FixIt 作者，喜欢瞎折腾、造轮子、写东西，分享一些前端开发中的所见、所闻、所思。","home_page_url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/","language":"en","icon":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/apple-touch-icon.png","favicon":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/favicon.ico","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/images/avatar.jpg"}],"items":[{"title":"WAMPServer 自定义网站根目录等设置","date_published":"2019-07-12T18:44:36&#43;08:00","date_modified":"2026-07-03T18:39:48&#43;07:00","id":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/wamproot/","url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/wamproot/","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://gravatar.loli.net/avatar/fee47a2f4f2cc71f99a02b0a73ecfee0?s=32&amp;d=mp"}],"tags":["WAMP","PHP","windows","server"],"summary":" 使用 WAMPServer 时自定义网站根目录。\n","content_html":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e使用 WAMPServer 时自定义网站根目录。\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e"},{"title":"ubuntu + windows 双系统默认启动项设置","date_published":"2019-03-21T12:48:30&#43;08:00","date_modified":"2026-07-03T18:39:48&#43;07:00","id":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/windefault/","url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/windefault/","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://gravatar.loli.net/avatar/fee47a2f4f2cc71f99a02b0a73ecfee0?s=32&amp;d=mp"}],"tags":["linux","windows","ubuntu"],"image":"/posts/windefault/images/1.png","summary":" 双系统默认启动项是 Ubuntu，而日常使用最多的还是 Windows，所以说很不方便，一不小心就开机到 Ubuntu 去了。今天来设置一下。\n","content_html":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e双系统默认启动项是 Ubuntu，而日常使用最多的还是 Windows，所以说很不方便，一不小心就开机到 Ubuntu 去了。今天来设置一下。\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e"},{"title":"win10,ubuntu 双系统时间不一致","date_published":"2019-03-15T14:28:10&#43;08:00","date_modified":"2026-07-03T18:39:48&#43;07:00","id":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/ubuntutime/","url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/ubuntutime/","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://gravatar.loli.net/avatar/fee47a2f4f2cc71f99a02b0a73ecfee0?s=32&amp;d=mp"}],"tags":["ubuntu","linux","windows"],"summary":" 我的 Ubuntu 和 Windows 双系统是 Ubuntu 是第一启动项，所以总是开机忘记点下键，一进 Ubuntu 系统时间就不对了（总是少了 8 小时），回到 Windows 时间也是错的。知道是错的调整一下还好。忘记调了有时候真的会误事。比如说 git 版本控制提交会遇到问题种种等。\n","content_html":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e我的 Ubuntu 和 Windows 双系统是 Ubuntu 是第一启动项，所以总是开机忘记点下键，一进 Ubuntu 系统时间就不对了（总是少了 8 小时），回到 Windows 时间也是错的。知道是错的调整一下还好。忘记调了有时候真的会误事。比如说 git 版本控制提交会遇到问题种种等。\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e"},{"title":"windows 上搭建 web 服务器","date_published":"2018-10-26T21:56:18&#43;08:00","date_modified":"2026-07-03T18:39:48&#43;07:00","id":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/","url":"https://nfl-alvis.github.io/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/","authors":[{"name":"Lruihao","url":"https://github.com/Lruihao","avatar":"https://gravatar.loli.net/avatar/fee47a2f4f2cc71f99a02b0a73ecfee0?s=32&amp;d=mp"}],"tags":["server","windows"],"summary":" 我用的 win10\n0.1 打开控制面板 选择并进入“程序”，双击“启用或关闭 Windows 服务”，在弹出的窗口中选择“Internet Information Services”下面所有地选项，点击确定后，开始更新服务。\n打开控制面板 0.2 查看 更新完成后，打开浏览器，输入http://localhost或者127.0.0.1回车，如果此时出现 IIS7 欢迎界面，说明 Web 服务器已经搭建成功。\n","content_html":"\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e我用的 win10\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"heading-element\" id=\"打开控制面板\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0.1 打开控制面板\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"#%e6%89%93%e5%bc%80%e6%8e%a7%e5%88%b6%e9%9d%a2%e6%9d%bf\" class=\"heading-mark\"\u003e\n    \u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n  \u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e选择并进入“程序”，双击“启用或关闭 Windows 服务”，在弹出的窗口中选择“Internet Information Services”下面所有地选项，点击确定后，开始更新服务。\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png\" title=\"打开控制面板\" data-thumbnail=\"/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003e打开控制面板\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e打开控制面板\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" src='/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/1.png' alt=\"打开控制面板\" height=\"742\" width=\"1408\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003e打开控制面板\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch3 class=\"heading-element\" id=\"查看\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e0.2 查看\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003ca href=\"#%e6%9f%a5%e7%9c%8b\" class=\"heading-mark\"\u003e\n    \u003csvg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n  \u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e更新完成后，打开浏览器，输入\u003ccode\u003ehttp://localhost\u003c/code\u003e或者\u003ccode\u003e127.0.0.1\u003c/code\u003e回车，如果此时出现 IIS7 欢迎界面，说明 Web 服务器已经搭建成功。\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png\" title=\"查看\" data-thumbnail=\"/ctf-writeups/posts/web-server-win/images/2.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003e查看\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e查看\u003c/p\u003e"}]}